  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK706">
<l>aṭuttatu kāṭṭum paḷiṅkupō ṉeñcaṅ</l>
<l>kaṭuttatu kāṭṭu mukam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the mirror reflects what is near so does the face show what is uppermost in the mind.</l>
            </lg>
